#
# === Variables
#
# [*ensure*]
#   The version of the package to install
#   Could be "latest", "installed" or a pinned version
#   This matches "ensure" from Package
#
# [*package*]
#   The package name in your provider
#
# [*provider*]
#   The provider used to install the package
#
